{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848998681,"sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","part":{"id":"prt_d78d93507001Ju07aq3q58sFFM","messageID":"msg_d78d91681001rTbWRqjsO00MZb","sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-81996a7d564b4325b33f9369304c58db","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775848998662,"end":1775848998679}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848998684,"sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","part":{"id":"prt_d78d931bb001u8C2s5r1pdaZ2v","messageID":"msg_d78d91681001rTbWRqjsO00MZb","sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6e3a99ad72a74edaac0e8bc226912a4d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-009/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-009/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: [待填写: Router HTTP 反向代理核心的目的和动机]\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In Scope\n10: \n11: | Deliverable | Description |\n12: |-------------|-------------|\n13: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n14: \n15: ### Key Components\n16: \n17: [待填写]\n18: \n19: ### Out of Scope\n20: \n21: - [待填写]\n22: \n23: ## Impact Analysis\n24: \n25: ### Upstream Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Dependency | Impact |\n28: |------------|--------|\n29: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n30: \n31: ### Downstream Consumers\n32: \n33: | Consumer | Usage |\n34: |----------|-------|\n35: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n36: \n37: ### Breaking Change Considerations\n38: \n39: - [待填写]\n40: \n41: ## Alternatives Considered\n42: \n43: [待填写]\n44: \n45: ## Risks\n46: \n47: | Risk | Mitigation |\n48: |------|------------|\n49: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n50: \n51: ## Implementation Notes\n52: \n53: [待填写]\n54: \n55: ## References\n56: \n57: - [待填写]\n\n(End of file - total 57 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n[待填写: Router HTTP 反向代理核心的目的和动机]\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| [待填写] | [待填写] |\n\n### Key Components\n\n[待填写]\n\n### Out of Scope\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20