{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849012569,"sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","part":{"id":"prt_d78d9757b0015JVPd4K31UaMMD","messageID":"msg_d78d96033001hazWUXmlBBN48w","sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8b5ba233979843a1b910c08f169a0401","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/session-routing"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/session-routing</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\ndesign.md\nspec.md\n\n(2 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":"design.md\nspec.md","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/session-routing","time":{"start":1775849012559,"end":1775849012568}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849012575,"sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","part":{"id":"prt_d78d97cee001Up9m4h5tvF6uPn","messageID":"msg_d78d96033001hazWUXmlBBN48w","sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-83fd5fb74cee471c95b980aa2bbeef5b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-007 |\n8: | Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n17: \n18: - **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n19: - **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n20: \n21: 控制器将：\n22: 1. 监听 CRD 资源的创建、更新、删除事件\n23: 2. 根据 CR spec 协调实际状态向期望状态收敛\n24: 3. 管理底层 Pod、Service、ConfigMap 等工作负载资源\n25: 4. 更新 CR status 以反映当前状态\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n30: \n31: ### 2.1 In Scope\n32: \n33: 1. **Controller 框架搭建**\n34:    - 使用 `controller-runtime` 框架 (sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n35:    - 集成 client-go 生成的客户端代码\n36:    - 实现 Reconcile 循环\n37: \n38: 2. **AgentRuntime 控制器**\n39:    - 监听 AgentRuntime CR 的变更\n40:    - 创建/更新/删除关联的 Kubernetes 资源 (Pod, Service, ConfigMap, Secret)\n41:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, PodStatus, Endpoint 等\n42:    - 支持多副本部署策略\n43: \n44: 3. **CodeInterpreter 控制器**\n45:    - 监听 CodeInterpreter CR 的变更\n46:    - 管理解释器容器的生命周期\n47:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, ResourceUsage 等\n48: \n49: 4. **通用功能**\n50:    - Event 记录 (Normal/Warning)\n51:    - Finalizer 处理 (资源清理)\n52:    - OwnerReference 设置 (级联删除)\n53:    - 领导选举 (Leader Election) 支持多实例部署\n54: \n55: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n56: \n57: - Webhook (Validating/Mutating) - 由独立 AR 处理\n58: - CRD 定义本身 - 假设已存在\n59: - 具体业务逻辑 (Agent 执行、解释器逻辑) - 由其他模块处理\n60: - 监控指标暴露 - 由独立 AR 处理\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n65: \n66: ### 3.1 新增文件\n67: \n68: ```\n69: pkg/workloadmanager/\n70: ├── controller.go              # 控制器入口，注册 Manager\n71: ├── agentruntime_controller.go # AgentRuntime Reconciler 实现\n72: ├── codeinterpreter_controller.go # CodeInterpreter Reconciler 实现\n73: ├── reconciler.go              # 通用 Reconciler 辅助函数\n74: ├── status.go                  # 状态更新辅助函数\n75: ├── resource_builder.go        # Kubernetes 资源构建器\n76: ├── predicates.go              # Event 过滤谓词\n77: └── suite_test.go              # 控制器集成测试\n78: ```\n79: \n80: ### 3.2 依赖关系\n81: \n82: ```\n83: pkg/workloadmanager\n84:     ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go (已生成)\n85:     ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (需引入)\n86:     ├── k8s.io/api\n87:     ├── k8s.io/apimachinery\n88:     └── k8s.io/client-go\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### 3.3 与现有模块交互\n92: \n93: | 模块 | 交互方式 |\n94: |------|----------|\n95: | pkg/apis/runtime | 读取 CR 类型定义 |\n96: | client-go | 使用生成的 Clientset、Informer、Lister |\n97: | cmd/manager | 作为控制器入口点启动 |\n98: \n99: ### 3.4 风险与缓解\n100: \n101: | 风险 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n102: |------|------|----------|\n103: | 控制器重启导致短暂不可用 | Medium | 使用 Leader Election 确保单实例 |\n104: | CRD 版本兼容性 | Low | 使用 apiVersion 检查 + conversion webhook |\n105: | 大规模资源性能问题 | Medium | 使用 Informer 缓存 + WorkQueue 限流 |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n110: \n111: ### 4.1 方案 A: controller-runtime (推荐)\n112: \n113: **实现方式**: 使用 sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime 框架\n114: \n115: **优点**:\n116: - Kubernetes 官方推荐方案\n117: - 内置 Informer、WorkQueue、Leader Election\n118: - 与 kubebuilder 生态兼容\n119: - 社区活跃，文档完善\n120: - 原生支持 webhook\n121: \n122: **缺点**:\n123: - 框架较重，学习曲线稍陡\n124: - 调试复杂度高\n125: \n126: ### 4.2 方案 B: client-go 原生实现\n127: \n128: **实现方式**: 使用 client-go 的 Informer + WorkQueue 手写控制器\n129: \n130: **优点**:\n131: - 完全控制实现细节\n132: - 无额外依赖\n133: - 更轻量\n134: \n135: **缺点**:\n136: - 需要手写大量样板代码\n137: - 需要自己实现 Leader Election\n138: - 维护成本高\n139: - 与社区最佳实践脱节\n140: \n141: ### 4.3 方案 C: KUDO\n142: \n143: **实现方式**: 使用 KUDO (Kubernetes Universal Declarative Operator)\n144: \n145: **优点**:\n146: - 声明式操作定义\n147: - 内置状态机\n148: \n149: **缺点**:\n150: - 项目已停止维护\n151: - 学习成本高\n152: - 不适合简单控制器\n153: \n154: ### 4.4 方案选择\n155: \n156: **选择方案 A (controller-runtime)**\n157: \n158: 理由:\n159: 1. 官方推荐，社区支持好\n160: 2. 与现有 client-go 生成的代码无缝集成\n161: 3. 为后续 webhook、monitor 集成铺路\n162: 4. 降低维护成本\n163: \n164: ---\n165: \n166: ## 5. 设计要点\n167: \n168: ### 5.1 Reconcile 循环伪代码\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: func (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n172:     // 1. 获取 CR\n173:     ar := &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}\n174:     if err := r.Client.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, ar); err != nil {\n175:         return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(err)\n176:     }\n177: \n178:     // 2. 检查 DeletionTimestamp (Finalizer 处理)\n179:     if !ar.DeletionTimestamp.IsZero() {\n180:         return r.handleDeletion(ctx, ar)\n181:     }\n182: \n183:     // 3. 确保 Finalizer 存在\n184:     if err := r.ensureFinalizer(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n185:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n186:     }\n187: \n188:     // 4. 同步期望状态\n189:     result, err := r.sync(ctx, ar)\n190:     if err != nil {\n191:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n192:     }\n193: \n194:     // 5. 更新 Status\n195:     if err := r.updateStatus(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n196:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n197:     }\n198: \n199:     return result, nil\n200: }\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### 5.2 状态机\n204: \n205: ```\n206: ┌─────────┐    Create    ┌─────────┐\n207: │  None   │ ──────────> │ Pending │\n208: └─────────┘             └────┬────┘\n209:                              │\n210:                         PodCreated\n211:                              │\n212:                              v\n213:                        ┌─────────┐\n214:                        │ Running │\n215:                        └────┬────┘\n216:                             │\n217:                     Failed/Succeeded\n218:                             │\n219:                             v\n220:                       ┌──────────┐\n221:                       │ Terminated│\n222:                       └──────────┘\n223: ```\n224: \n225: ---\n226: \n227: ## 6. 实施计划\n228: \n229: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估工时 |\n230: |------|------|----------|\n231: | P1 | 搭建 controller-runtime 框架 | 2d |\n232: | P2 | 实现 AgentRuntime 控制器 | 3d |\n233: | P3 | 实现 CodeInterpreter 控制器 | 2d |\n234: | P4 | 单元测试 + 集成测试 | 2d |\n235: | P5 | Leader Election + 监控 | 1d |\n236: \n237: **总计**: ~10 人天\n238: \n239: ---\n240: \n241: ## 7. 参考文档\n242: \n243: - controller-runtime: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\n244: - client-go 生成的代码: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n245: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n\n(End of file - total 245 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-007 |\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n\n- **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n- **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775849012565,"end":1775849012574}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849012579,"sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","part":{"id":"prt_d78d97957001jg6ZkexYIu0j7X","messageID":"msg_d78d96033001hazWUXmlBBN48w","sessionID":"ses_287270f86ffeSemVNN1czfTDNb","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ba975acde01e4e1c84875bd8de207cfb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: [待填写: K8s Reconciler 控制器的目的和核心职责]\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In Scope\n10: \n11: | Deliverable | Description |\n12: |-------------|-------------|\n13: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n14: \n15: ### Out of Scope\n16: \n17: - [待填写]\n18: \n19: ## Impact Analysis\n20: \n21: ### Upstream Dependencies\n22: \n23: | Dependency | Impact |\n24: |------------|--------|\n25: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n26: \n27: ### Downstream Consumers\n28: \n29: | Consumer | Usage |\n30: |----------|-------|\n31: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n32: \n33: ### Breaking Change Considerations\n34: \n35: - [待填写]\n36: \n37: ## Alternatives Considered\n38: \n39: [待填写]\n40: \n41: ## Risks\n42: \n43: | Risk | Mitigation |\n44: |------|------------|\n45: | [待填写] | [待填写] |\n46: \n47: ## Implementation Notes\n48: \n49: [待填写]\n50: \n51: ## References\n52: \n53: - [待填写]\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n[待填写: K8s Reconciler 控制器的目的和核心职责]\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| [待填写] | [待填写] |\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- [待填写]\n\n## Impact Analysis\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-007/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775849012563,"end":1775849012577}}}}
